<p>There is a typographical error in the legend for Figure 1.</p>
<p>The statement “they can result from either <bold>d.</bold> a clonally heterogeneous infection or <bold>e.</bold> a mixed infection” should instead read “they can result from either <bold>d.</bold> a mixed infection or <bold>e.</bold> a clonally heterogeneous infection”.</p>
